WEBVTT

00:00.344 --> 00:02.231
Previously on,<i> "The</i>
<i>Arrangement"...</i>

00:02.718 --> 00:05.487
In two weeks, I am marrying
the love of my life.

00:05.650 --> 00:08.051
<i>Your costar clearly
has feelings for you.</i>

00:08.053 --> 00:09.085
<i>I've seen it.</i>

00:09.087 --> 00:10.211
We could fix this.

00:10.211 --> 00:11.274
The man just fired me.

00:11.846 --> 00:13.212
Ah, so you wanna be an actor?

00:13.214 --> 00:14.813
<i>Do me a favor. Leave him alone.</i>

00:14.815 --> 00:16.038
Mason was my friend.

00:16.038 --> 00:17.249
I should be the one to
look out for her son.

00:17.251 --> 00:18.554
She talked about you a lot.

00:18.651 --> 00:20.184
About what a screw-up I am?

00:20.785 --> 00:21.819
What is this?

00:22.093 --> 00:23.168
A role.

00:23.168 --> 00:25.983
- What's this about?
- Julie Woolth. I found her.

00:26.096 --> 00:29.197
I will always credit IHM
with changing my life.

00:29.452 --> 00:31.337
She's lying. You have to go back

00:31.338 --> 00:32.743
and get Julie to talk to you.

00:33.540 --> 00:34.546
Hello?

00:34.908 --> 00:36.441
Terence will ruin everything...

00:36.443 --> 00:38.541
My marriage, my career.

00:38.812 --> 00:40.745
Julie, we need to talk.

00:41.056 --> 00:42.254
Let them stay.

00:42.254 --> 00:43.620
Terence did this to you?

00:43.623 --> 00:45.803
- Terence? No.
- Then who?

00:46.396 --> 00:47.659
What do you know?

00:47.927 --> 00:49.086
Everything.

00:50.930 --> 00:52.664
It just escalated between us,

00:52.664 --> 00:53.647
fast.

00:54.600 --> 00:57.188
I said something to him.
He said something back.

00:58.036 --> 01:00.042
And whatever he said, it just...

01:00.172 --> 01:01.519
Set you off,

01:02.441 --> 01:03.631
like in Venice.

01:04.275 --> 01:06.642
No, no, not like that, it was different.

01:07.273 --> 01:08.457
Different how?

01:08.514 --> 01:10.680
Ah, just, back then, I...

01:10.682 --> 01:11.888
I was different.

01:12.441 --> 01:13.517
It was like...

01:13.519 --> 01:15.385
It was like I was having
an out-of-body experience.

01:15.387 --> 01:17.075
I don't know how else to explain it.

01:18.123 --> 01:19.521
I don't even remember what I did.

01:19.546 --> 01:20.847
I just remember the feeling.

01:23.616 --> 01:25.022
You don't remember?

01:26.865 --> 01:29.099
It's not like I was having
a... a rage blackout,

01:29.101 --> 01:31.215
but my... my brain, I just...

01:35.374 --> 01:36.673
You still haven't told me

01:36.675 --> 01:38.041
why you were even looking for Aaron.

01:38.043 --> 01:39.464
He's in a wheelchair.

01:39.545 --> 01:41.251
- I know...
- No, you don't know.

01:41.794 --> 01:44.072
You don't because you hid him away...

01:44.300 --> 01:45.712
You and Terence.

01:45.834 --> 01:47.501
After what happened with Evan,

01:47.770 --> 01:48.769
what did you do?

01:48.771 --> 01:50.214
Are you crazy?

01:50.306 --> 01:52.072
He tried to rape me, again.

01:52.074 --> 01:53.273
- And you killed him.
- Stop it.

01:53.275 --> 01:54.675
Did you face the consequences?

01:54.677 --> 01:56.476
That was a completely different situation.

01:56.478 --> 01:57.667
When that guy was arrested for it,

01:57.667 --> 01:59.600
did you step forward?

01:59.867 --> 02:01.656
No, you didn't,

02:01.988 --> 02:03.600
because you were scared.

02:04.256 --> 02:07.381
Survival, self-preservation...
It's human nature.

02:09.050 --> 02:10.919
And Terence preserved you...

02:12.089 --> 02:14.847
Your future, your career.

02:15.096 --> 02:16.694
He made it all go away.

02:18.609 --> 02:19.820
So that's it?

02:22.409 --> 02:24.245
That's the reason for the contract.

02:25.362 --> 02:26.445
It's not me.

02:27.442 --> 02:28.557
It's you...

02:29.615 --> 02:30.934
To protect you,

02:31.969 --> 02:33.485
to protect your brand.

02:33.987 --> 02:35.410
There were a lot of reasons

02:35.413 --> 02:36.823
for the contract, Megan.

02:40.851 --> 02:42.347
Why were you looking for him?

02:44.088 --> 02:46.371
Why did you and Zach go
looking for Julie and Aaron?

02:48.752 --> 02:51.117
Please, tell me.

02:56.975 --> 02:58.654
We were trying to hurt Terence.

03:00.510 --> 03:02.687
So you've been lying?

03:03.009 --> 03:04.326
All these months?

03:04.576 --> 03:06.294
About IHM, yeah.

03:06.511 --> 03:08.032
You should've told me.

03:10.248 --> 03:13.022
If I did, would you have
turned your back on Terence?

03:15.153 --> 03:17.324
You're a true believer.

03:18.990 --> 03:20.990
And the last time I told you something,

03:20.992 --> 03:22.599
you turned me in.

03:23.690 --> 03:25.278
You gonna do that again?

03:26.465 --> 03:28.215
You gonna help Aaron go public?

03:29.603 --> 03:32.070
You can't keep a secret
from the world forever.

